                    d="M288 109.3V352c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32s-32-14.3-32-32V109.3l-53.3 53.3c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3l109.3-109.3c12.5-12.5 32.8-12.5 45.3 0l109.3 109.3c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3s-32.8 12.5-45.3 0L288 109.3zM64 352H192c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64s64-28.7 64-64H448c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V192c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H352c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32h96c0 0 0 0 0 0v96c0 0 0 0 0 0H64c0 0 0 0 0 0V160h96c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H64C28.7 96 0 124.7 0 160V288c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64z" />
